io.wcm.qa.glnm.selectors.base

Interface NestedSelector

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Selector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNestedSelectorBase, FixedValueNestedSelector, SelectorFromLocator

    public interface NestedSelector
extends Selector
    A nested Selector can have a parent and children. If it has a parent, its standard representation will have CSS relative to parent.
    Since:
    1.0.0
